Description_lang: Broodtwister Ovi'nax injects a cocktail of unstable substances into his target, inflicting $s2 Nature damage and an additional $s1 Nature damage every $t1 sec for $d.Upon expiration the chemicals react, inflicting additional Nature damage based on the target's missing health. This damage is reduced the healthier the target is.
AuraDescription_lang: $s1 Nature damage inflicted every $t1 sec.Upon expiration, inflicts Nature damage based on your missing health.
